:HELP NAME=STRSRMGEN.Status route access maintenance - Help
:XH3.Status route access maintenance
:ISCH ROOTS='Status route access maintenance'.
Status route access maintenance

:P.
The Status route access maintenance function enables you to define status
routes. Status route access is used to authorize employees.

:P.
Please consult the
:LINK PERFORM='DSPHELP CONSTAT OMSCONHD'.
Status concepts
:ELINK.
for more information about status routes.
