:P.
:LINK PERFORM='DSPHELP STRSRM'.
General Information.
:ELINK.

:P.
The :PK.Maintain Status Route:EPK. display enables you to perform
the chosen action on a status route.
:EHELP.

.*   .............................................................   *.
.*   : Display 2  FMSTRC (Status route code)                     :   *.
.*   :                                                           :   *.
.*   : Help Area : 08 028  08 037                                :   *.
.*   :...........................................................:   *.

:HELP NAME='OMH02004/FMSTRC'.Status route - Help
:P.
The unique name of the status route is displayed or filled in here.
:P.
Follow this link to the
:LINK PERFORM='DSPHELP CONSTAT OMSCONHD'.
status concepts
:ELINK.
for more information on status routes.
:P.
Instead you may type in "*ALL". This means that the employee is going
to be authorized for every status route. If, at a later stage, a
new status route will be added to the status route file, it will
be added automatically to this employee profile.
:P.
Using F4 results in a selection display with all available status
routes.
:EHELP.

